Program: Discovery
Title: The abalone and family planning
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwjb
Last Broadcast Date: 23 October 1995
How the abalone's evolution might help with the development of contraception. Because they produce lots of eggs and sperm they can be studied easily. Also in the programme, a mushroom from the age of the dinosaurs, a new way of treating epilepsy with heart disease medication and a cosmic space-station vacuum cleaner being used on Mir. Show less